}
```

#### List Analytics Buckets

Retrieves all analytics buckets in your project with optional filtering and pagination:

```typescript
const { data, error } = await analytics.listBuckets({
  limit: 10,
  offset: 0,
  sortColumn: 'created_at',
  sortOrder: 'desc',
  search: 'prod',
